        "kind": "source",
        "text": "\"The first music takes place in reason, the second in fantasy, and the third in words. Thence follows song, and after that the movement of the fingers in sound. Lastly the movement of the whole body in gymnastics or dancing. Thus the music of the soul is led by steps to all the limbs of the body.\""
