        "kind": "source",
        "text": "His explication is an “ontology” because it addresses wujūd and explains exactly what\nthe word implies as soon as we recognize that it is aname for the unknowable\nEssence that is named by all the names, the Existence whose quiddity is to have\nno quiddity."
