        "text": "Icannot give any assurance as to the manner in which the meanings attached to asymbol will appear to aparticular person. Ido not have enough information from other people to characterize any particular way as \"typical\". In my own case, they come in two or three ways, depending on the amount of power Ihave managed to invoke and how high above my normal level of consciousness Ihave managed to raise my awareness."
